title: Polyacanthia flavipes
text: Polyacanthia flavipes is a species of <a href="beetle">beetle</a> in the family <a href="Cerambycidae">Cerambycidae</a>. It was described by White in 1846, originally under the genus "<a href="Lamia%20%28genus%29">Lamia</a>". It is known from <a href="New%20Zealand">New Zealand</a>.
